&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Working closely with waiver members, caregivers, and other stakeholders in the business, the Care Managers goal will be to provide a seamless Customer Service experience, while ensuring that our clients are receiving the care they need.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
