&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Coordinate patient services and care with pharmacies, insurance companies, hospital discharge planning, family caregivers, and other providers&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
